01:13.646 --> 01:14.963
Unh!

01:14.965 --> 01:16.464
Agh!

01:21.304 --> 01:23.489
No way.
I'm not doing it.

01:23.491 --> 01:25.357
What makes you think you have a choice?

01:25.359 --> 01:28.310
You have to kill vampires to
complete the hunter's mark.

01:28.312 --> 01:29.811
Mark equals cure.

01:29.813 --> 01:31.947
You're in a bar full
of almost vampires,

01:31.949 --> 01:33.648
so get your hunt on.

01:33.650 --> 01:35.751
Screw you. You said I
wouldn't have to kill

01:35.753 --> 01:36.919
any innocent people.

01:36.921 --> 01:39.004
Jeremy, they're not people.

01:39.006 --> 01:41.123
Enough! Have at it,
or else.

01:41.125 --> 01:44.343
I don't take orders from you, dick.

01:44.345 --> 01:46.879
Hunters can't be compelled.

01:50.183 --> 01:53.001
You're right.
I can't compel you,

01:53.003 --> 01:54.887
but if your conscience
is getting in the way,

01:54.889 --> 01:57.306
then allow me to make this easy for you

01:57.308 --> 01:59.641
because I can compel them.

02:03.062 --> 02:04.863
I'm gonna give you a
two-minute head start.

02:04.865 --> 02:07.499
Then I'm gonna send every
vampire in here after you.

02:07.501 --> 02:12.070
You kill them, or they
kill your friend... Matt.

02:12.072 --> 02:13.121
Wait a second.

02:13.123 --> 02:15.707
No, no. You turn them,
he kills them.

02:15.709 --> 02:16.992
That was the deal, Klaus.

02:16.994 --> 02:18.877
I'm taking artistic license.

02:18.879 --> 02:21.196
You know he can't take them
all on at the same time.

02:21.198 --> 02:23.415
With you as his coach, he'll be fine.

02:23.417 --> 02:26.418
It's Matt I'm worried about.

02:26.420 --> 02:29.304
Ehh.

02:29.306 --> 02:30.889
Jeremy, go get
the weapons out of the car.

02:30.891 --> 02:32.724
I'll be right behind you.

02:34.093 --> 02:35.510
Go with him.

02:36.896 --> 02:38.564
If I hear an engine start,

02:38.566 --> 02:40.482
I'll kill Matt myself!

02:44.237 --> 02:46.054
Are you ok?

02:46.056 --> 02:47.389
Yeah. I just
need a second.

02:47.391 --> 02:48.824
We don't have a second.

02:48.826 --> 02:50.943
They can smell your blood.
We need to go.

02:53.864 --> 02:56.031
Don't hesitate.
You're lucky it was me.

02:56.033 --> 02:57.866
Otherwise, you two would be dead.

02:57.868 --> 02:59.034
You set us up.

02:59.036 --> 03:00.335
I'm was trying to get
this thing over with.

03:00.337 --> 03:01.837
You're the one that pissed off Klaus.

03:01.839 --> 03:04.039
Now you have to fight
your way out of it.

03:04.041 --> 03:05.757
Where are the other vampires?

03:05.759 --> 03:07.259
They're newbies. They're still
trying to figure out how to track,

03:07.261 --> 03:10.545
which means you have two
seconds to get ready to fight.

03:10.547 --> 03:11.930
The lake house is this way.

03:11.932 --> 03:13.849
If we can get there, they
won't be able to get inside.

03:13.851 --> 03:16.551
Wait. You want to run?

03:16.553 --> 03:19.754
They're gonna kill Matt.

03:19.756 --> 03:22.474
Fine. Get out of here.
I'll slow them down.

03:38.074 --> 03:39.825
Jeremy, where are you?

03:39.827 --> 03:41.793
Keep going.
We're almost there.

03:54.507 --> 03:56.124
Are you ok?

03:57.510 --> 03:59.061
Oh, my God.

03:59.063 --> 04:01.063
Get to the house!
Hurry!

04:08.071 --> 04:09.821
Jeremy, what's going on?

04:09.823 --> 04:11.306
They're coming.

04:17.940 --> 04:23.234
<font color="#40bfff">Sync & corrections by <font color="#FFA500">wilson0804</font></font>
